ISLAMABAD, Dec 09 (APP):Islamabad Electric Supply Company (IESCO) on Monday issued a power suspension programme for Tuesday for various areas of its region due to installation of AMI meters, necessary maintenance and routine development work.
According to IESCO Spokesperson, the power supply of different feeders and grid stations would remain suspended for the period from 9:00 AM to 2:00 PM, Islamabad Circle: Tumair, Shaheed-e-Millat, Lehtrar Road, Zia Masjid, Highway, G-8/1, F-10 Markaz, G-10/1, Chashnop, I-10/2, G-13/2-1, Pir Mehar Ali Shah, T&T, Sunny Bank, Cecil, Bariyan, Kotli Sattian, Tret, Athal feeders. Rawalpindi City Circle: Saidpur Road, National Market, Muzammil Town, Khanna-II, Service Road, Airport, Quaidabad, Fawara Chowk, Tahmasmabad, Gawalmandi, Jamia Masjid, Westridge, Eidgah, Liaquat Bagh, Allama Iqbal, Madina Colony, Officer Colony, MME Complex, Lakho Road, I-14/2 & 3, Ratta, Alamabad feeders. Rawalpindi Cantt Circle: Mall Road, Adamjee Road, Rahimabad, PWT-II, Humak, Gulistan Colony, Pindi Board, Humayun-I, Rose Lane, Ranyal, Gulshan Shaheed, Chungi 22, Rajar, Old Rawat, New Rawat, SUPARCO, AOWHS, Kahuta City-I, KRL, THQ, Kallar Syedan, Pindori Chowk, Ghazan Khan, Mandra-II, PAEC, Kiranb Kaswal, Nishan-e-Haider, CB Khan-II feeders. Attock Circle: Taxila, HMC Road, Sher Shah Suri, Wahdat Colony (D/C), Kohsar Colony (D/C), Valley, Model Town, Kashif Gul, Mix Industry, Shahia, Rashid Minhas, AWC Housing, Munirabad, Islampura, Pathar Garh, Musa, Shamsabad, Qaziabad, Hatian, Power Channel Co., Barazai, Shakar Dara, Shadi Khan (D/C), Sirkah (D/C), Attock Cantt, Malho Wali, Naka Kalan, Mianwala, Bahtar, Jand-I, Jand-II, Kamrial, Galyal, Laniwala, Amanpur feeders. Jhelum Circle: Abbas Pura, Zubair Shaheed, F-3 (Gul Afshan), Mandi Bahawal, Shamsabad, Akram Shaheed, Pakhwal, Dina Theri (Rohtas), Chamala, Captain Nisar Shaheed, Nathwala, Safdar Shaheed, F-12 (Singhui), Colonel Muhammad Akram, Ward No. 8, Kalia, Chappar Sharif, Thakra, Kangar Thati feeders. Chakwal Circle: Tharpal, Millat Chowk, Maingan, Dharanka, Islamia Chowk, Doltala, Latifal, Dhrogi Rajgaan, Sarkal, Basharat, Rawal, Ahmadabad, KS Mines, Jalalpur, Pipli, Dhurnal, Sakka, Talagang City, Akhwal, Bilalabad, Darot, Mial, Wanhars f